section
  ul#productInfoAccordion(role='tablist').info-accordion
    li#overviewHeading(role="tab", v-if='$parent.item.translation && $parent.item.translation.description')
      a#overviewCollapseLabel(data-toggle="collapse", href='#overviewCollapse',
      aria-controls='overviewCollapse', aria-expanded='false').collapse-title Product Overview
      #overviewCollapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='overviewCollapseLabel',
      data-parent="#productInfoAccordion").collapse
        .col-12
          br
          p(itemprop='description', v-html="$parent.item.translation.description")
          br
          br
    li#detailsHeading(role="tab")
      a#detailsCollapseLabel(data-toggle="collapse", href='#detailsCollapse',
      aria-controls='detailsCollapse', aria-expanded='false').collapse-title Product Details
      #detailsCollapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='detailsCollapseLabel',
      data-parent="#productInfoAccordion").collapse
        br
        .col-12
          .row(v-if="$parent.item")
            .col-5
              p.small
                strong Product
            .col-7
              p.small(v-if="$parent.item.designer") {{ $parent.item.designer.designer_name }} {{ $parent.item.model_name }}
          .row(v-if="$parent.item")
            .col-5
              p.small
                strong Product SKU
            .col-7
              p.small
                span(itemprop='sku') SS{{ $parent.item.item_number / 100 }}
          .row
            .col-5
              p.small
                strong Suitable for
            .col-7
              p.small
                i.fi-torso.fa-lg.blue
                | &nbsp;
                i.fi-torso-female.fa-lg.pink
          .row
            .col-5
              p.small
                strong Single Vision
            .col-7
              p.small
                i.fa.fa-check.fa-lg.green(aria-hidden='true')
          .row
            .col-5
              p.small
                strong Progressives
            .col-7
              p.small
                i.fa.fa-check.fa-lg.green(aria-hidden='true')
                em
                  | Freeform varifocal from&nbsp;
                  strong {{calculatePrice(1247.95/33.47, false, true)}}
          .row
            .col-5
              p.small
                strong Spring hinge
            .col-7
              p.small
                i.fa.fa-times.fa-lg.red(aria-hidden='true')
          .row
            .col-5
              p.small
                strong Available as Sunglasses
            .col-7
              p.small
                i.fa.fa-check.fa-lg.green(aria-hidden='true')
          br
          p.small
            i.fa.fa-thumbs-o-up.fa-lg.blue(aria-hidden='true')
            | &nbsp;&nbsp;
            strong 12 Months Warranty
          p.small
            i.fa.fa-gift.fa-lg.blue(aria-hidden='true')
            | &nbsp;&nbsp;
            strong Includes Case & Cloth
          .text-center
            hr.short-hr
            p.small.info-links
              router-link(to='/price-list/', target='_blank').blue-ul Our Lens Prices
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/info/shipping-delivery/', target='_blank').blue-ul Production & Delivery
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/info/returns/', target='_blank').blue-ul 14-Day Returns

        br
        br
    li#helpHeading(role="tab")
      a#helpCollapseLabel(data-toggle="collapse", href='#helpCollapse',
      aria-controls='helpCollapse', aria-expanded='false').collapse-title Product Help
      #helpCollapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='helpCollapseLabel',
      data-parent="#productInfoAccordion").collapse
        br
        .frame-help
          .col-12
            h3 Will this frame suit me?
            p.smaller
              | Not sure if this frame is right for you? See our guide to face shapes & frame styles&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/info/face-shapes/').blue-ul here
              | .
            br
          .col-12
            h3 What lenses should I choose?
            p.smaller
              | Our virtual dispenser can recommend you the perfect lenses for your prescription - You can also find out more about our lenses&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/guides/lenses/').blue-ul here
              | &nbsp;or see our lens price list&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/price-list/').blue-ul here
              | .
            br
          .col-12
            h3 How and where are my glasses made?
            p.smaller
              | All prescription glasses are made to an incredibly high standard in one of our labs. Find out more&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/about-us/lab/').blue-ul here
              | .
            br
        .sunglasses-help
          .col-12
            h3 Will these sunglasses suit me?
            p.small
              | Not sure if these sunglasses will suit you? Take a look at our guide to face shapes & frame styles&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/info/face-shapes/').blue-ul here
              | .
            br
          .col-12
            h3 Different sun lens technologies
            p.small
              | Unsure of the difference between polarised or transitions/photochromic technologies? Our handy guide to lenses explains all&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/guides/lenses/').blue-ul here
              | .
            br
          .col-12
            h3 What sunglasses do I need for driving?
            p.small
              | We always recommend polarised lenses for driving. Check out our guide to choosing safe sunglasses&nbsp;
              router-link(to='/guides/how-to-choose-safe-sunglasses-for-driving/').blue-ul here
              | .
            br
        br
        br
    li#reviewsHeading(role="tab")
      a#reviewsCollapseLabel(data-toggle="collapse", href='#reviewsCollapse',
      aria-controls='reviewsCollapse', aria-expanded='false').collapse-title Customer Reviews (71)
      #reviewsCollapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='reviewsCollapseLabel',
      data-parent="#productInfoAccordion").collapse
        .container.px-3
          br
          .text-center
            p.smaller
              | 78 Review(s) -&nbsp;
              a.blue-ul(href='#', rel='nofollow') Add your review
            p.smaller
              strong 94%
              | &nbsp;of customers recommend this product&nbsp;
              em (64 of 68)
            br
            .pr-review.row.mb-3
              .col-12.col-md-4.review-meta.text-left
                a(name='review_id')
                p.review-author(itemprop='author', itemscope='', itemtype='http://schema.org/Person')
                  strong
                    span(itemprop='name') J Spencer
                    | ,&nbsp;
                    span(itemprop='nationality') IE
                p.smallest
                  em POSTED: 23rd August 2017
                div(itemprop='reviewRating', itemscope='', itemtype='http://schema.org/Rating')
                  .product-rating.my-1
                    p
                      strong OVERALL
                    .rateit(data-rateit-value='4.00',
                    data-rateit-ispreset='true',
                    data-rateit-readonly='true',
                    data-rateit-mode="font")
                  .review-helpful.my-3.mx-0
                    | Was this review useful? Â 
                    span.text-nowrap
                      a.helpful(data-helpful='17561_1', href='#')
                        i.fa.fa-thumbs-up
                        | &nbsp;Yes
                      a.helpful(data-helpful='17561_0', href='#')
                        i.fa.fa-thumbs-down
                        | &nbsp;No
              .col-12.col-md-8.review-body.text-left
                .container-fluid
                  .row
                    .product-rating.float-left
                      p
                        strong
                          em Style
                      .rateit(data-rateit-value='5.00',
                      data-rateit-ispreset='true',
                      data-rateit-readonly='true',
                      data-rateit-mode="font")
                    .product-rating.float-left
                      p
                        strong
                          em Quality
                      .rateit(data-rateit-value='3.00',
                      data-rateit-ispreset='true',
                      data-rateit-readonly='true',
                      data-rateit-mode="font")
                    .product-rating.float-left
                      p
                        strong
                          em Value
                      .rateit(data-rateit-value='4.00',
                      data-rateit-ispreset='true',
                      data-rateit-readonly='true',
                      data-rateit-mode="font")
                  hr.row.mt-0
                  .row
                    p(itemprop='name')
                      strong Quality Matches the Price
                  .row
                    p.small(itemprop='description') The left arm has broken, but it was good for the price. They lasted for three months.
                  hr.row
                  .row
                    p.small
                      span.text-nowrap
                        | [
                        strong  Fit -
                        |  As expected ]&nbsp;&nbsp;
                      br
                      span.text-nowrap [ I would recommend this product to others ]
            .row
              #reviewShowMore.btn.big-orange-button + Show 5 more
          br
          br
